Current yElo ratings for the WTA tour. This list includes only those players who have won five or more tour-level, tour-level qualiyfing, men's challenger, or ITF $50K+ matches in the current calendar year.
yElo only considers current year results for each player, as if we had no previous information to draw upon. It's like the official "Race" rankings, but with the Elo magic of properly adjusting for strength of opponent and taking into account the increased certainty that comes with larger samples.
Learn more about Elo here, and read about the yElo concept here.
